        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This ring is utilitarian in design\u2014indicating its martial use. Its band is decorated only with a simple, sharp-edged sculpture on the band\u2019s center. While wearing this ring, you add your level to your attack rolls with all weapons with which you are untrained.",
